==English==
===Etymology===
From Latin ''[[ablatus]]'', past participle stem of ''[[auferre]]'' "to take away".

===Verb===
{{en-verb|ablat|ing}}

# {{transitive}} To [[remove]] or [[decrease]] something by the process of [[ablation]].
# {{intransitive}} To [[undergo]] ablation.

